The new Russian has finished the renovation, invites his sidekick to the show. He wandered around the apartment and said:
- Everything would be fine, but I looked into the bathroom, the tile is completely out of the question. It's kind of small, and even gray-brown.
New Russian:
- Well, follow me! A small, brown one...
they went into the bathroom, a new Russian and said:
- Read what is written on the tile.
The sidekick is reading:
- G4500 3.5 GHz INTEL PENTIUM...
